==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Uncircumstandtial
<hw>Un*cir`cum*stand"tial</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Not circumstantial; not entering into minute particulars.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not important; not pertinent; trivial.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Uncity</ent>⟦br⟧
